title: N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 16 §§ 892-3.3 - Effective competition
content:
N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 16 §§ 892-3.3 - Effective competition

State Regulations

Only the rates for basic cable service of a cable
television system that is not subject to effective competition as defined in
47
CFR section
76.905
may be regulated by a
municipality or the commission. In the absence of a demonstration to the
contrary, cable systems are presumed not to be subject to effective
competition. Notes
N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 16
§§
892-3.3
